{"tid":1474884,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企人幫忙置業 買定唔買","createTime":"2019-08-15T10:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T10:39:35.000Z","uid":77235,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67e147b89948a75ed922299704c2f36ca26717e3","tid":1474884,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"我本來諗住買樓買啲細單位 有張床訓下就夠 供樓壓力都冇咁大<br />\n但屋企人建議買大間啲 最多供唔掂既部份佢地出<br />\n應唔應該聽佢地講 因為擔心將來有機會鬧不和 冇左佢地既幫助會供唔掂"},{"pid":"ca48831d30561d82d4ea466a1afbaddfb523db62","tid":1474884,"uid":162713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:15:57.000Z","msg":"你預之後抬唔起頭做人<br />\n一有咩爭執 就拎唔幫你供樓嚇你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然 你有信心唔會嘈架<br />\n就梗係好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c32b1fb256b054b1c01a8e28d774da6d06d062b","tid":1474884,"uid":126330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67e147b89948a75ed922299704c2f36ca26717e3","tid":1474884,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:12:47.000Z","msg":"我本來諗住買樓買啲細單位 有張床訓下就夠 供樓壓力都冇咁大<br />\n但屋企人建議買大間啲 最多供唔掂既部份佢地出<br />\n應唔應該聽佢地講 因為擔心將來有機會鬧不和 冇左佢地既幫助會供唔掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"等於供手相讓個春袋比屋企人<br />\n比定唔比？<br />\n<br />\n講真：如果同屋企人關係麻麻地就真係唔好搏，<br />\n除非你可以肯定佢地同你點嘈都會一齊供落去 或者 你可以忍到幾十年，咁咪去馬囉"},{"pid":"7fc256649a94406f9d54d5a168c9ba901b6eaf4d","tid":1474884,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:19:34.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n靠自己最穩陣"},{"pid":"78d448ede468b95af2a7937988a4a508fc24fced","tid":1474884,"uid":40743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"寫你名only"},{"pid":"89b41e4dd0d210d5338f3639cda94bcadbe4bb4d","tid":1474884,"uid":77235,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca48831d30561d